<h2 id="cl_0">文章分为以下3部分</h2><h3>1、开箱晒物</h3><h3>2、我是怎么使用的</h3><h2 id="cl_1">一、开箱晒物</h2><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_2/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/14/5f5edd7b36f6b4804.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">使用的顺丰发过来的<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_3/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/14/5f5edd7b3d0d71881.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">里面也包裹的很严实，完全不用担心会坏掉<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_4/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7b5020a547.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">产品正面纯白设计加上产品实物照，很简约很小米风<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_5/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7ca99f66432.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">侧面是产品的功能介绍</p><p itemprop="description"><strong>1.轻巧便携、还是无线的</strong></p><p itemprop="description">0.5kg仅主机重量，比<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/baowenbaolengbei/" target="_blank">保温杯</a>还纤细。</p><p itemprop="description"><strong>2.13000Pa 澎湃吸力</strong></p><p itemprop="description"><a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/dianchi/" target="_blank">电池</a>满电量时，高档运行状态，整机真空度实测可达到13100Pa，抵挡运行状态，整机真空度实测可达7760Pa。</p><p itemprop="description"><strong>3.88000转/分钟 无刷马达</strong></p><p itemprop="description">电池满电量时，高档位电机转速实测可达88000转/分钟。</p><p itemprop="description"><strong>4.一键倒尘功能，干净利落的操</strong></p><p itemprop="description">米家随手<a class="seo_link" href="https://www.smzdm.com/fenlei/xichenqi/" target="_blank">吸尘器</a>实现单手一键操作，这样单手操作既方便又能避免脏污与人体接触。</p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_6/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7c9aba2308.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">包装背面是产品的详细介绍和生产地址<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_7/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7c9a7ea6417.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">侧边是封条<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_8/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7d2a4561150.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">打开后，也有泡沫纸包装好的<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_9/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7d5346e2686.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">产品包括主机一台、毛刷吸头、缝隙吸头、Type-C充电线、说明书一本<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_10/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7d6f6c63866.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_11/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7e9e2fa4691.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_12/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://qnam.smzdm.com/202009/14/5f5edd7ea6f00584.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_13/' target='_blank'><img alt="懒人神器米家随手吸尘器，肥仔躺也能打扫卫生" src="https://am.zdmimg.com/202009/14/5f5edd7ebc5937504.jpg_e680.jpg" title="" /></a></p><p itemprop="description">顶部是集尘盒的开关，开关需要向下搬动，在按一下就可以打开集尘盒了<br/></p><p itemprop="description"><a href='https://post.smzdm.com/p/ax0x96md/pic_14/' target='_blank'><